(332, 0, 259, NULL, 1, 'remove obsolete img border from tinymce.php (deprecated in html4, obsolete in html5)', '<p>When inserting an image while using tinymce the element border="0" is automatically added to the html.</p>\n\n<p>eg</p>\n\n<p><a target="_blank" href="/images/someting.png"><img border="0" src="/images/someting.png" alt="something" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>\n\n<p>it is even added if you specify a border in the insert image popup</p>\n\n<p><a target="_blank" href="/images/someting.png%22"><img src="/images/someting.png%22" alt="something" border="0" width="400" height="164" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>\n\n<p>The border element was deprecated in HTML4 and is obsolete in HTML5.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-07-04 11:13:02', '2012-09-01 09:22:09', '2012-09-01 09:34:49', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/259.diff'),
