(339, 0, 266, NULL, 1, 'JRequest::getInt returns string', '<p>JRequest::getInt returns a string instead of a integer when magic_quotes is on.<br>\ncause of issue <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/blob/master/libraries/joomla/environment/request.php#L155">https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/blob/master/libraries/joomla/environment/request.php#L155</a> , don''t know if JInput is also affected by this bug.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-07-09 23:35:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-10 07:08:15', NULL),
