(436, 0, 363, NULL, 1, 'Removes <strong> from module chrome markup', '<p><strong> is a semantic element, not a presentational one. For stylistic purposes simply set font-weight in css instead. It''s use in this context is incorrect.</strong></p>\n\n<p>See: <a href="http://html5doctor.com/i-b-em-strong-element/">http://html5doctor.com/i-b-em-strong-element/</a> for details.</p>\n\n<p>Semantically, it would be preferable to wrap the module header in a   element too of course. </p>\n\n<p>I shall submit an additional PR with suggested improvements to the module markup. </p>\n\n<p>Thanks.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-07 08:43:26', '2012-09-07 09:10:51', '2012-09-07 09:10:51', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/363.diff'),
