(651, 0, 578, NULL, 1, 'Overflow', '<p>From Tracker <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485</a> </p>\n\n<p>Log in to Joomla! 3 administration using IE8 or IE9. Create a new menu item. Click Select on Menu Item Type. This prevents the list from overlapping.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-11-29 22:08:40', '2012-11-29 23:47:45', '2012-11-30 00:10:44', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/578.diff'),
(652, 0, 579, NULL, 1, 'Overflow', '<p>From Tracker <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485</a></p>\n\n<p>Log in to Joomla! 3 administration using IE8 or IE9. Create a new menu item. Click Select on Menu Item Type. This prevents the list from overlapping.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-11-29 23:53:07', '2012-11-30 00:27:31', '2012-11-30 00:27:31', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/579.diff'),
(653, 0, 580, NULL, 1, 'Overflow 3', '<p>From Tracker <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485</a></p>\n\n<p>Log in to Joomla! 3 administration using IE8 or IE9. Create a new menu item. Click Select on Menu Item Type. This prevents the list from overlapping.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-11-30 00:28:26', '2012-11-30 00:31:16', '2012-11-30 00:31:16', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/580.diff'),
(654, 0, 581, NULL, 1, 'Overflow 4', '<p>From Tracker <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29485</a></p>\n\n<p>Log in to Joomla! 3 administration using IE8 or IE9. Create a new menu item. Click Select on Menu Item Type. This prevents the list from overlapping.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-11-30 00:37:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-11-30 00:37:15', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/581.diff'),
(655, 0, 582, NULL, 1, 'Constants aren''t consistant', '<p>Strange title, right? You would thing that within an application, when a constant is defined, it will always be referring to the same thing - but that''s not the case in Joomla.</p>\n\n<p>Depending on where you are, <code>JPATH_TEMPLATES</code> could point to <code>{root}/templates</code> OR it could point to <code>{root}/administrator/templates</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Also, <code>JPATH_BASE</code> could point to the root directory OR <code>{root}/administrator</code></p>', 3, 10, '2012-11-30 16:07:22', '2012-12-01 06:04:47', '2012-12-01 06:04:47', NULL),
