(1458, 4969503, 181, 'okonomiyaki3000', 'comment', '<p>I would be happy to do that if only I could stay logged in to joomlacode long enough. I have posted here multiple times about this problem. Am I the only one? I log in, click a link or two and suddenly I''m logged out again. It happens no matter what browser I use, whether I access from home or work, mac or windoze. Does that site actually function for some people? What''s the secret? </p>', '2012-04-05 06:53:07'),
