(1499, 5116606, 191, 'mbabker', 'comment', '<p>This code should actually be removed.  The <code>$_observers</code> array in JDispatcher is protected and unable to be accessed from the indexer helper.</p>\n\n<p>The best practice is for plugins to check for the <code>com_finder.indexer</code> context.  Otherwise, there really isn''t anything that can be done within the indexer''s code.</p>', '2012-04-13 15:12:32'),
