(1538, 5770051, 210, 'rmcdaniel', 'comment', '<p>When I started, com_menus didn''t have an access.xml. I created it and then moved the component permissions to the new access.xml from config.xml so it would look more like com_content. Looking at the commit, I don''t think the access.xml I created got added. Sorry for the confusion, I''m a bit new to Git.</p>', '2012-05-17 18:04:14'),
