(2105, 9508021, 475, 'mbabker', 'comment', '<p>We''ve already added modifications to the bootstrap.js files for one of the other conflicts, so I personally don''t see a huge issue with modifying that file directly so long as the change is clearly indicated in the file.  Check <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/blob/master/media/jui/js/bootstrap.js#L603">here</a> for what we did for the Dropdown plugin.  And <a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/blob/master/media/jui/js/bootstrap.js#L496">this line</a> fixes a conflict we ran into with MooTools and jQuery in the Collapse plugin.</p>', '2012-10-16 21:39:51'),
