(2299, 11319980, 600, 'okonomiyaki3000', 'comment', '<p>Ah, tabs. Nice touch. That callback logger is pretty great, eh? </p>\n\n<p>One additional thing I was thinking was to queue the log messages between requests so that if you submit a form or something that then redirects, you will not miss the logs for that redirected request.</p>', '2012-12-13 02:31:06'),
