(125, 0, 52, NULL, 1, 'CLI tweaks', '<p>Clean up the CLI files</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Move Finder CLI out of it''s own folder and rename it</li>\n<li>Move garbage_cron to an executable PHP file and refactor it to use JApplicationCLI</li>\n<li>Sync Finder CLI bootstrap to framework''s</li>\n<li>Use JApplicationCLI::getInstance</li>\n</ul>', 3, 10, '2011-12-22 05:50:59', '2012-01-22 16:21:46', '2012-01-22 16:21:46', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/52.diff'),
