(180, 0, 107, NULL, 1, 'mod_menu invalid rendering of items of type alias and url', '<p>In Joomla 2.5 mod_menu rendering of menu items of type alias and url calls htmlspecialchars for item url.<br>\nBut this is already processed by helper of mod%menu by calling JRoute::_() function. It results in invalid urls.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-01-28 23:06:13', '2012-02-01 09:23:06', '2012-02-01 09:23:06', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/107.diff'),
