(231, 0, 158, NULL, 1, 'fix bug #27852', '<p>This bug report manage to fix joomla update when stream http layer is off (allow_url_fopen disabled in php.ini).<br>\nThe fix add other http layers to the joomla update (like curl).</p>\n\n<p>more info: <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=27852">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=27852</a></p>', 3, 1, '2012-03-19 17:20:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-03-19 17:20:04', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/158.diff'),
