(289, 0, 216, NULL, 1, 'Category view only processes content triggers on the first few articles in the list', '<p>Due to the leading article and intro article usage in the IF statement surrounding the content triggers it results in only the first, for example, 5 articles being processed with triggers. If those triggers are used to alter the authors name for example then only the first 5 will actually change.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-05-29 12:36:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-05-31 12:25:44', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/216.diff'),
