(331, 0, 258, NULL, 1, 'Menu Manager: Edit Menu Item - Default Page option for Default Menu Link is unlogical ', '<p>Situation:<br>\n1. Create a bunch of Menu Items<br>\n2. Set one of them(e.g. Home) as "Default Page"<br>\n3. Now open them Menu Item:Home(Menu Manager: Edit Menu Item - View)<br>\n4. Try to set the "Default Page" to "No"</p>\n\n<p>The result:<br>\nSave failed with the following error: At least one menu item has to be set as Default.</p>\n\n<p>Solution maybe:<br>\nMaybe a checkbox, remove the decission between yes or no!</p>\n\n<p>Best regards</p>', 3, 1, '2012-07-01 10:13:23', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-01 10:13:44', NULL);
