(369, 0, 296, 28039, 1, '[#28039] Using chrome for Android generates an error in browser.php', '<p>Tracker item<br><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28039">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28039</a></p>\n\n<p>This is a merge of <br><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/issues/942" class="issue-link" title="fix bug #28039">joomla/joomla-platform#942</a><br><a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-platform/issues/946" class="issue-link" title="Joomla CMS [#28039] Using Chrome for Android generates an error in browser.php (line 562) ">joomla/joomla-platform#946</a></p>\n\n<p>This change is already in the master.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-07-28 15:01:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-28 15:01:15', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/296.diff'),
