(385, 0, 312, NULL, 1, 'Fix type attributes not required in html5. Thanks @nternetinspired', '<p>Issue reported by <a href="https://github.com/nternetinspired" class="user-mention">@nternetinspired</a> in the template9 branch:<br><a href="https://github.com/Joomla3-Admin-template/joomla-cms/issues/114" class="issue-link" title="Type attributes are not required in html(5)">Joomla3-Admin-template/joomla-cms#114</a></p>\n\n<p>To enable the html5 mode in the template use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>JFactory::getDocument()-&gt;setHtml5(true);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>The type attributes will dissappear.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-08-18 00:56:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-08-20 14:11:49', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/312.diff'),
