(405, 0, 332, 28764, 1, '[#28764] user notes category is not properly nested in the assets table', '<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28764">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=28764</a></p>\n\n<p>This pull replaces pull 297. (<a href="https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/issues/297" class="issue-link" title="Usernotes3">joomla/joomla-cms#297</a>)</p>', 3, 10, '2012-08-26 15:29:31', '2012-10-08 00:37:41', '2012-10-08 00:37:41', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/332.diff'),
(406, 0, 333, NULL, 1, 'Fixed modules modChrome_html5 coding style. Added support not to use "span" at all', '<p>I fixed coding style of modules.php file as discussed here <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/GyZf9_LgDDU">https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/GyZf9_LgDDU</a></p>\n\n<p>Also implemented not to use "Bootstrap size" parameter at all, because adding "spanX" to a class sometimes spoils the output: <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/WACu4ymBd5o">https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups=#!topic/joomla-dev-general/WACu4ymBd5o</a></p>', 3, 10, '2012-08-27 11:18:26', '2012-10-01 12:20:22', '2012-10-01 12:20:22', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/333.diff'),
