(462, 0, 389, NULL, 1, 'Joomla update Purge button', '<p>If - for some reason - the update feed/stream have been unavailable at least once, the stream is marked as disabled.</p>\n\n<p>If this happens to any 2.5/3.0 sites, it will require a push on "Purge" under extension updates.<br>\nNot very intuitive when joomla updates is separated out.</p>\n\n<p>This is a purge button which resets last check time and enables site update stream again.</p>\n\n<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29162">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29162</a></p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-15 19:27:22', '2012-09-22 22:59:47', '2012-09-22 22:59:47', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/389.diff'),
