(478, 0, 405, NULL, 1, 'Fatal error in libraries/joomla/html/sliders.php', '<p>Hi,<br>\nwhen clicking on Warning in Admin, we get a fatal error around line 110.<br>\nThjis has been corrected in Platform :</p>\n\n<pre><code>//$options = self::getJSObject($opt);\n\n$options = JHtml::getJSObject($opt);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Re : github version joomla-joomla-cms-3.0.0_beta1-81</p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-17 11:52:05', '2012-09-18 08:25:26', '2012-09-18 08:25:26', NULL),
(479, 0, 406, NULL, 1, 'Login module fix', '', 3, 10, '2012-09-17 13:30:54', '2012-10-05 19:35:10', '2012-10-05 19:35:10', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/406.diff'),
(480, 0, 407, NULL, 1, 'Sidebar', '<p>Attempt at fixing <a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29050">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29050</a></p>\n\n<p>Added JHtmlSidebar and JLayout classes to start replacing JSubMenuHelper<br>\nand Submenu backend module<br>\nUpdated plugins manager main view and extensions manager default view to<br>\nuse the new class, as proof of concept</p>\n\n<p>This is proof of concept. All backend extensions should be modified to take advantage of new class if approved.</p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-17 14:04:21', '2012-09-21 19:50:31', '2012-09-21 19:50:31', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/407.diff'),
(481, 0, 408, NULL, 1, 'com_contact single contact view for logged-in user', '<p>I believe that the single contact view for com_contact should also allow the display of the contact information attached to the logged in user, because the contact component is more flexible than the profile plugin.</p>\n\n<p>The fix is easy:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>make the user field in the contact menu item optional</li>\n<li>default to the logged in user''s ID</li>\n<li>only throw error if neither of the IDs is defined (from the request trough menu item params or from the session from the logged-in user)</li>\n</ul>', 3, 1, '2012-09-18 08:54:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-09-18 08:54:21', NULL),
(482, 0, 409, NULL, 1, 'Jcode 29223', '<p>Fixes #29223, and adds helper to load bootstrap css files in one go</p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-18 10:14:14', '2012-09-18 10:20:26', '2012-09-18 10:20:26', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/409.diff'),
(483, 0, 410, NULL, 1, 'Jcode 29223', '<p>Fixes joomlacode #29223, adds a css loader for bootstrap and a /media/cms/css/bootstrap.css fils where bugfixes for bootstrap can be added</p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-18 11:03:07', '2012-09-19 12:31:09', '2012-09-19 12:31:09', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/410.diff'),
(484, 0, 411, NULL, 1, 'Patch 1', '<p>CAN THIS BE DELETED/IGNORED PLEASE?<br>\nIt should have gone into "Platform", which it now has.<br>\nThanks.</p>\n\n<p>This patch makes unions work in J! 2.5.7.</p>\n\n<p>Since the file has been backported from the 12.1 api, it should/could make them work there too?</p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-18 21:17:54', '2012-09-20 15:03:53', '2012-09-20 15:03:53', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/411.diff'),
