(487, 0, 414, NULL, 1, 'Move installer and updater libraries to cms', '<p>CMS Tracker:<br><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29235">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29235</a></p>\n\n<p>Platform discussion;<br><a href="https://groups.google.com/group/joomla-dev-platform/browse_thread/thread/1d6727a66eca9927">https://groups.google.com/group/joomla-dev-platform/browse_thread/thread/1d6727a66eca9927</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Platform pull request will be created following successful CMS testing.</p>\n\n<p>Testing of installer is successful.  Testing of updater currently fails.</p>\n\n<p>The code change currently is a simple move of the installer and updater directories from libraries/joomla to libraries/cms.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-09-19 12:33:58', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-09-19 12:33:58', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/414.diff'),
(488, 0, 415, 28956, 1, '[#28956] No error message when saving a menu item with no title', '<p>Replaced visual clue-only (adding "invalid" class) which was missing<br>\nfrom template anyway by simple alter box when trying to save a menu item<br>\nwith an empty title<br>\nNote: template should have:<br>\n.invalid {<br>\n    color: red;<br>\n    font-weight: bold;<br>\n}</p>\n\n<p>input.invalid {<br>\n    border: 1px solid red;<br>\n}<br>\nfor the bad field(s) to be displayed. Also, I removed the JS to highlight invalid field, for consistency</p>', 3, 1, '2012-09-19 16:47:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-09-20 20:05:31', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/415.diff'),
