(506, 0, 433, 29211, 1, '[#29211] Isis: Jumping table rows on mouseover', '<p>Navigate e.g. to Extensions -&gt; Module Manager and hover over the title column in different rows. Next to the title, a dropdown toggler is displayed which causes the table row to "jump", meaning that it changes its height.</p>\n\n<p><a href="http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29211">http://joomlacode.org/gf/project/joomla/tracker/?action=TrackerItemEdit&amp;tracker_item_id=29211</a></p>', 3, 10, '2012-09-22 19:34:27', '2012-09-22 19:41:25', '2012-09-22 19:41:25', NULL),
