(514, 0, 441, NULL, 1, 'RTL Testing Hack', '<p>Adds an RTL english dummy configuration[all translations fall through to the default english configuration] for easy testing by lame english speakers like me who don''t know any other languages.  Using this, a developer can set just his account into RTL mode to see what is actually be displayed without affecting display for anyone else.</p>', 3, 1, '2012-09-24 21:11:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-09-27 20:37:57', 'https://github.com/joomla/joomla-cms/pull/441.diff'),
